snippet.title: Eyra, the Crow Maiden Promo Trailer (Version A)
snippet.description:
Eyra, the Crow Maiden, a brand new NES game by Second Dimension. The kickstater campaign is now live at: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/seconddimension/eyra-the-crow-maiden-a-new-adventure-for-the-nintendo-nes/?ref=youtube


Video by: J. Criscuolo
